  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safeguarding and Empowering Communities through Upgrading Agricultural Skills, Disaster Preparedness and Environmental Management (SECURE)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To support communities who have recently become victims of, or are vulnerable to hydro-meteorological disasters and increase their resilience to future disasters.

This project will provide:
1. Agricultural rehabilitation for riverside farmers.
2. Strengthen the capacity of communities to manage and mitigate risks.
3. Improve the health of affected communities through distribution of hygiene kits and hygiene training.</narrative>
  </description>
